      <section class="c-section">
        <div class="_c-container">
          <h1 class="c-section__title">What is Basis?</h1>
          <div class="_c-row _c-row--margin _c-row--md-fill">
            <div class="_c-row__col _c-row__col--1-1 _c-row__col--md-1-3">
              <section class="p-media _u-text-center">
                <div class="p-media__figure">
                  <i class="fa fa-code fa-3x"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="p-media__body">
                  <h1 class="p-media__title">Clean code development</h1>
                  <div class="p-media__content">
                    The Basis classes have prefix. And code style is <a href="http://csswizardry.com/2013/01/mindbemding-getting-your-head-round-bem-syntax/" target="_blank">BEM (MindBemding)</a> and using Stylus. You can use it as CSS framework or Stylus mixin library.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </section>
            </div>
            <div class="_c-row__col _c-row__col--1-1 _c-row__col--md-1-3">
              <section class="p-media _u-text-center">
                <div class="p-media__figure">
                  <i class="fa fa-mobile fa-3x"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="p-media__body">
                  <h1 class="p-media__title">Responsive &amp; Mobile first</h1>
                  <div class="p-media__content">
                    The grid system is flexbox based. So it's simple and excellent than the float layout! Same height box, Reverse grid, Equal spacing layout and more.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </section>
            </div>
            <div class="_c-row__col _c-row__col--1-1 _c-row__col--md-1-3">
