                </div>
                <div class="p-media__body">
                  <h1 class="p-media__title">Lightweight &amp; Minimum style</h1>
                  <div class="p-media__content">
                    The Basis style is lightweight and minimum. It just may not be enough, but so overwritable.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </section>
            </div>
